data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath split foyer on large private corner lot! This home offers an open floor plan with freshly updated flooring and recently rebuilt back porch. 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the upstairs level. 1 bedroom and laundry on the lower level. Plenty of storage available or the option to fully finish the basement. There is also a 2 car garage with tons of space and cabinetry! NO HOA!
